{"tid":2151830,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"好過去搶系列：美心食品勁賺納稅人3.2億元津貼","createTime":"2020-08-11T15:04:52.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-11T15:41:45.000Z","uid":51546,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"84138c328889ad1c84822a416dabcc9297db6af2","tid":2151830,"uid":51546,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-11T15:04:52.000Z","msg":"「保就業」計劃第七批領取工資補貼僱主名單今（11日）公布，涉及約16,900名僱主，補貼額約62.3億元。「保就業」計劃目前已發放的第一期工資補貼合共涉及約432億元，涵蓋接近146,100名僱主及承諾受薪僱員總人數約187萬；秘書處正安排向下一批約7500名成功申請僱主發放約26億元補貼，承諾受薪僱員人數約116,000人。<br />\n<br />\n．美心食品有限公司／$321,144,783／13,456<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n．永旺香港（AEON）百貨有限公司／$59,943,624／3013<br />\n<br />\n．香港航空有限公司／$77,122,791／2940<br />\n<br />\n另外，第二輪「防疫抗疫基金」下的建造業「長散工」保就業計劃，共接獲1800多份建造業僱主提交的申請。建造業議會現正進行審批，預計補助金可於8月中旬開始發放。"},{"pid":"648964d19d999fd9a78df5d410440a9f3ec60fd5","tid":2151830,"uid":51546,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-11T15:05:43.000Z","msg":"罷買？？<br />\n直接問政府攞錢囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ae2f4aaf5d63e7d44872c0533c402bdb1e208b52","tid":2151830,"uid":51546,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-11T15:41:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}